---
// Component Imports
import MainLayout from "../layouts/MainLayout.astro";
import "../styles/styles.css";
---

<MainLayout>
  <section class="mt-lg dark:bg-neutral500" id="loreal1">
    <h1 class="sm:text-lg text-md font-helvetica2 dark:text-primary100">
      L'Oreal For the Future
    </h1>
    <p class="max-w-[750px] text-xs font-helvetica mt-md dark:text-neutral200">
      In an effort to spread out the sustainability initiatives made by Lâ€™Oreal
      Group, a campaign was made. The centerpiece of the campaign is a
      compelling video that seeks to share L'Oreal's vision and inspire action.
    </p>
    <img class="rounded-md mt-md" src="../images/salon1.png" alt="" />
    <p class="max-w-[750px] text-xs font-helvetica mt-lg dark:text-neutral200">
      The movie follows a consumer thoughout a visit to a salon. Along the way,
      the different sustanaible initiatives are presented. While reminding the
      viewer of the previous initiatives, the movie should show that this is a
      new program that stands on top of the commitments taken earlier in the
      value chain..
    </p>
  </section>
  <section class="mt-xl dark:bg-neutral500 para_container" id="loreal2">
    <h2
      class="text-md dark:text-neutral200 font-helvetica2 sm:text-lg text-right para"
    >
      storyboard<span class="text-accent200">.</span>
    </h2>
    <div class="story_images mt-md">
      <img src="../images/Billede2.png" alt="" class="story rounded-sm" />
      <img src="../images/Billede3.png" alt="" class="story rounded-sm" />
      <img src="../images/Billede4.png" alt="" class="story rounded-sm" />
      <img src="../images/Billede5.png" alt="" class="story rounded-sm" />
      <img src="../images/Billede6.png" alt="" class="story rounded-sm" />
      <img src="../images/Billede7.png" alt="" class="story rounded-sm" />
      <img src="../images/Billede8.png" alt="" class="story rounded-sm" />
      <img src="../images/Billede9.png" alt="" class="story rounded-sm" />
      <img src="../images/Billede10.png" alt="" class="story rounded-sm" />
    </div>
  </section>
  <section class="mt-xl dark:bg-neutral500 para_container" id="animations">
    <h2 class="font-helvetica2 dark:text-neutral200 text-md sm:text-lg para">
      animations<span class="text-accent200">.</span>
    </h2>
    <p class="max-w-[750px] dark:text-neutral200 text-xs font-helvetica mt-md">
      L'Oreal For The Future is enriched by an array of graphical animations
      that are designed to captivate, educate, and inspire viewers. These
      animations played an instrumental role in conveying the campaign's complex
      messages in a simple, engaging, and visually appealing manner.
    </p>
    <div class="animations_videos mt-md">
      <video
        class="rounded-sm"
        plays-inline
        autoplay
        loop
        muted
        src="../video/water.mp4"></video>
      <video
        plays-inline
        autoplay
        loop
        muted
        class="rounded-sm"
        src="../video/waste.mp4"></video>
      <video
        plays-inline
        autoplay
        loop
        muted
        class="rounded-sm"
        src="../video/energy.mp4"></video>
    </div>
  </section>
  <section class="mt-xl dark:bg-neutral500 para_container" id="deliverables">
    <h2
      class="font-helvetica2 dark:text-neutral200 text-md sm:text-lg text-right para"
    >
      deliverables<span class="text-accent200">.</span>
    </h2>
    <p class="max-w-[750px] text-xs dark:text-neutral200 font-helvetica mt-md">
      The "L'Oreal For The Future" campaign was strategically disseminated
      through a series of powerful deliverables, comprising a long format video
      and three shorter cutdowns, each dedicated to the crucial environmental
      pillars of "water", "waste", and "energy".
    </p>
    <div class="deliver_videos mt-md">
      <video
        plays-inline
        controls
        class="rounded-sm"
        src="../video/cutdown_water.mp4"></video>
      <video
        plays-inline
        controls
        class="rounded-sm"
        src="../video/cutdown_waste.mp4"></video>
      <video
        plays-inline
        controls
        class="rounded-sm"
        src="../video/cutdown_energy.mp4"></video>
    </div>
  </section>
  <section class="mt-xl dark:bg-neutral500 para_container" id="results">
    <h2 class="font-helvetica2 dark:text-neutral200 text-md sm:text-lg para">
      results<span class="text-accent200">.</span>
    </h2>
    <p class="max-w-[750px] text-xs dark:text-neutral200 font-helvetica mt-md">
      The "L'Oreal For The Future" campaign's commitment to sustainability and
      innovation was recognized at the Danish Beauty Awards, where it was
      honored with the prestigious "Green Award". This award is a testament to
      L'Oreal's exemplary efforts towards implementing sustainable practices
      within the beauty industry.
    </p>
    <img class="rounded-md mt-md" src="../images/lorealgreen.png" alt="" />
  </section>
  <!-- <script>
    import "../scripts/loreal.js";
  </script> -->
</MainLayout>
